* RVM
Ruby Version Manager - makes version management and dependencies much easier
rvm

* MVC
** Model
** View
** Controller

* Rails router - config/routes.rb
** Rails router dispatches requests to the controller based on the URI

* Make app root
** rails new <app name>

* Startup WEBrick web server
rails server

* Scaffolding - code generation
rails generate scaffold User name:string email:string

* create the sqlite db tables 
bundle exec rake db:migrate
